title: 01/22 Fantasy Football Podcast: Sunday Reactions; 2017 Breakouts
description:
Philadelphia and New England are on to the Super Bowl! Let's recap the AFC (5:25) and NFC (10:32) Championship Games with some Fantasy thoughts and an offseason question for Jacksonville and Minnesota ... Check out our first voicemail question (25:30), as one of our listeners follows up on last week's A.J. Green analysis ... 2017 breakouts! What went right for Todd Gurley (27:30), a couple of Eagles studs (29:40), Mark Ingram (38:58), Marvin Jones (41:00), Tyreek Hill (43:14) and Adam Thielen (47:21) and what can we learn for 2018? ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
